data.description: Lovely 3 BR | 2 Bath| 2 Car garage home built in 2021 offers an open concept that is perfect for Entertaining Family & Friends! The Upgraded Kitchen opens to the Dining & Living Rooms which lead to the Screened Back Porch overlooking the spacious backyard. Kitchen offers granite counters, island with breakfast bar, 36'' cabinets w/ crown molding, pantry, S/S appliances including Refrigerator & Washer/Dryer. Owner's Suite features walk Shower, double vanity, large walk-in closet & linen closet. Entire house flooring is upgraded with luxury vinyl. Community with low HOA fees , County Only Taxes, and quick access to I-95 & Turnpike. Centrally located just 20 minutes to Tradition, Vero, or the Beach. Don't miss this opportunity to own this upgraded model ~ Call Today for your private showing! Sizes and Measurements are approximate. Buyer to verify all information.
